<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 15:15:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>欧盟改变氢能项目拍卖规则以限制中国的存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-changes-hydrogen-project-auction-rules-limit-chinese-presence-2024-09-27/</link><description>周五公布的新条款显示，欧盟宣布修改氢补贴拍卖规则，以限制欧盟在可再生能源供应链中对中国的依赖。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 14:51:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-changes-hydrogen-project-auction-rules-limit-chinese-presence-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车制造商比亚迪寻求进一步放宽墨西哥电动汽车关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-byd-seeks-further-easing-mexico-ev-tariffs-local-media-2024-09-27/</link><description>中国汽车制造商比亚迪正在寻求延长墨西哥政府对电动汽车进口的关税减免，一位高管在周五发表的《改革报》采访中表示，该公司计划在该国建立一家工厂。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 14:40:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-byd-seeks-further-easing-mexico-ev-tariffs-local-media-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对俄罗斯在中国生产攻击无人机的报道感到担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-concerned-by-report-russia-producing-attack-drones-china-2024-09-27/</link><description>欧盟发言人周五表示，有报道称俄罗斯正在为乌克兰战争开发中国支持的攻击无人机计划，“令人深感担忧”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 13:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-concerned-by-report-russia-producing-attack-drones-china-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国降低短期借贷成本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cuts-borrowing-cost-standing-lending-facility-2024-09-27/</link><description>中国央行周五晚间表示，将常备借贷便利（SLF）所有期限的借贷成本降低了 20 个基点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 12:42:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cuts-borrowing-cost-standing-lending-facility-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>一系列刺激措施推动中国相关股票上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-linked-stocks-climb-bevy-stimulus-measures-2024-09-27/</link><description>在美国上市的中国企业和专注于中国的基金股票周五大幅上涨，并有望在推动世界第二大经济体经济增长的一系列激进刺激措施的最新推动下继续强劲上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 12:16:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-linked-stocks-climb-bevy-stimulus-measures-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>即将上任的日本首相石破浩的“亚洲北约”理念对美国外交进行考验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/incoming-japan-pm-ishibas-asian-nato-idea-test-us-diplomacy-2024-09-27/</link><description>被任命为日本下一任首相的石破茂可能会提出让华盛顿陷入“亚洲北约”并在美国领土上驻扎日本军队的提议，从而重塑与东京最密切的联盟，这可能会给美国带来外交上的麻烦。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 11:31:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/incoming-japan-pm-ishibas-asian-nato-idea-test-us-diplomacy-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>日本称中国海军航母在太平洋停留7天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navy-carrier-spotted-pacific-seven-days-japan-says-2024-09-27/</link><description>日本防卫省周五表示，过去7天在太平洋发现中国海军“辽宁”号航母。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 10:14:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navy-carrier-spotted-pacific-seven-days-japan-says-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国降息和中国刺激措施引发更多亚洲私募股权交易的希望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-rate-cut-china-stimulus-spark-hope-more-asia-private-equity-deals-2024-09-27/</link><description>业内人士表示，美国降息和中国对市场的经济刺激计划将有利于亚洲私募股权交易，融资成本降低和市场情绪改善预计将使退出变得更容易。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 10:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-rate-cut-china-stimulus-spark-hope-more-asia-private-equity-deals-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国PCE关注中国加速反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-27/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 10:04:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>印度钢铁制造商集团警告美国征收关税后中国进口量增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indian-steelmaker-group-warns-rising-chinese-imports-after-us-tariffs-2024-09-27/</link><description>印度主要钢铁制造商组织周五警告称，在美国决定对中国进口钢铁征收25%的关税后，印度从中国的进口将进一步增加。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:54:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indian-steelmaker-group-warns-rising-chinese-imports-after-us-tariffs-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>对石破茂被选为日本下一任首相的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/reactions-shigeru-ishibas-selection-japans-next-pm-2024-09-27/</link><description>以下是对石破茂当选日本自民党党魁并使其下周接任首相的反应：</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:33:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/reactions-shigeru-ishibas-selection-japans-next-pm-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>舒适达制造商 Haleon 将增持中国合资企业股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sensodyne-maker-haleon-raise-stake-china-jv-2024-09-27/</link><description>英国消费者医疗保健公司 Haleon 周五表示，计划将其在中国合资企业中的股份从 55% 增加到 88%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:11:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sensodyne-maker-haleon-raise-stake-china-jv-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>台湾表示期待在石破浩领导下深化与日本的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-it-looks-forward-deepening-ties-with-japan-under-ishiba-2024-09-27/</link><description>赖清德领导的民进党周五表示，台湾总统赖清德期待在石破茂领导下深化与日本执政党的关系。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-it-looks-forward-deepening-ties-with-japan-under-ishiba-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警称菲律宾船只向仁爱礁运送物资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-says-philippine-vessel-took-supplies-second-thomas-shoal-2024-09-27/</link><description>中国海警周五表示，菲律宾派出一艘民用船向仁爱礁的一艘军舰运送日常必需品，北京称这艘军舰在南海有争议的水道上非法“搁浅”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 08:11:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-says-philippine-vessel-took-supplies-second-thomas-shoal-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国数据公布前，欧洲斯托克 600 指数跌破纪录高位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/stoxx-600-hits-record-high-china-driven-rally-set-weekly-gains-2024-09-27/</link><description>欧洲股市从周五早些时候触及的历史高位回落，因美国重要数据公布前市场普遍谨慎，不过盟可睐 (Moncler) 和奢侈品股的上涨限制了价格的进一步下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 07:37:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/stoxx-600-hits-record-high-china-driven-rally-set-weekly-gains-2024-09-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>